creator: Stadeo, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
We believe the "beautiful game" is best enjoyed socially, so we built the perfect home for fans to socialize around our favorite sport ("soccer" / "football" / "calcio").

Before, during or after games, Stadeo allows you to audio chat in real-time with friends, journalists, coaches, player and perfect strangers:
- Host private chats with family and friends
- Join open rooms with other fans like you
- Listen to the perspectives of famous opinion leaders
- Make new friends that share your passion from around the world

In addition to talking, Stadeo allows you to celebrate and joke around with interactions that bring the stadium or sports bar to your phone. Want to tease a fellow fan or the opposing team? Feel like starting a stadium chant? Stadeo is the place for you to engage with other fans as if you were in person.

Stadeo: the real-time audio home for soccer / football / calcio fans.
descriptionShort: Live Audio Football Fan Chat

title: Stadeo

descriptionHtml:
Join the real-time audio and text chat about the game and the culture with fans who know football. Live on Stadeo.

WHAT IS STADEO?

Stadeo helps you connect, chat and speak your mind live with fun, knowledgable football fans and communities.

When you join Stadeo, you literally have a say in building the world’s most social, real-time football community—your way.

- After the Game: Celebrate victories, bounce back from losses—talk about it real-time, live on Stadeo.
